Change the cart so that I can:
    - Use a path to clear out the cart items.
        - GET /cart/clear       clear out the cart items
    - Remove individual items from it.
        - GET /cart/remove/0
        - GET /cart/remove/1
        - GET /cart/remove/2
        - GET /cart/remove/3
        - GET /cart/remove/4
        - GET /cart/remove/5

    - Calculate the cart total everytime a new item is added to the cart.
    - Checkout and pay for the items in my cart.
        - GET /cart/confirm
        - GET /cart/pay
        - GET /cart/summary
